      <T n="text">0xC8CFA96A<!--String: "From Level 3 of the Noble Career your Sims can <b><font color='#199C2C'>Hold Court</font></b> from a throne anywhere within the Kingdom they live. This allows your Sims to listen to their visitors concerns or receive a promotion through a coronation ceremony to the next rank of the career if they qualify.\n\nFrom Level 4, Sims can Hold a Press Conference from a Podium object. During a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Press Conference</font></b> your Sims can give a Noble Speech to reach their subjects or dish the dirt on a Rival and reveal another Sim's scandal! If your Sim is currently in a Scandal they can also use the Press Conference to either Issue a Public Apology or Issue a Denial Statement to try reduce the duration of the Scandal."--></T>
